texts.text: CU58 was a version of Xbox One Edition released on December 3, 2019.[1] This was the final update for the Xbox One Edition. [edit]

Removed the "Download the latest version of Minecraft for FREE!" button from the menu and pause screen, but kept it in the options menu.
Updated all splashes to match with Bedrock Edition[2]
"Minecraft Xbox one edition just received an update. No word of what's inside, I imagine it's related to PS4 edition discontinuing in some way" – @ibxtoycat on Twitter, December 3, 2019
Minecraft Xbox One - Total Tour - Old Tutorial Worlds - AgentMindStorm - December 4, 2019
